comments.body: That does look like a cowbird! Brewer's Blackbird was recommended by the iNat ID engine, but cowbird certainly seems closer. Thank you!
I think that's a male Brown-headed Cowbird, but I can't see it well enough to say for sure. Male Brewer's should have a pale eye, and I can't see that here.
